.sp
Enable reporting packet ISO sequence number via \fIBT_SCM_PKT_SEQNUM\fP
CMSG on received packets.  Possible values:
.TS
box center;
l|l.
T{
Value
T}	T{
Description
T}
_
T{
\fB0\fP
T}	T{
Disable (default)
T}
_
T{
\fB1\fP
T}	T{
